data.description: Fantastic brick 2-story home in beautiful Stone Ridge. This house has it all! Enjoy this open floor plan with stunning kitchen - granite countertops, tons of cabinet space, large pantry, huge island and more. 4 spacious bedrooms including a desirable owners suite that contains a walk-in closet w/ built in shelves and a huge bathroom. Endless possibilities in the enormous unfinished basement. Private lot with fenced in yard + patio. Second floor laundry! Do not wait to see this one! One year home warranty included!
